# The command to move to the nearest stone resource executed successfully, but there was no output indicating the new position.
# Now that I'm at the stone resource patch, I will attempt to harvest stones from this location.

# I will try to harvest a quantity of 10 stones from the current position.
harvest_resource(nearest(Resource.Stone), quantity=10)  # Attempt to harvest 10 stones from the nearest stone resource.
